ted in Camille undertaking further study in Kinesiology which looks at our emotional, energetic, spiritual and physical health.\r\n\r\nRemedial Kinesiology is Camille\'s combination of remedial therapy and kinesiology to provide the client with a treatment that deals with the physical, emotional, energetic and spiritual blocks to good health and well being. Through the use of kinesiology Camille is able to determine the priority issue to be dealt with in any given session and works toward restoring balance on all levels.\r\n\r\nCamille offers a variety of single therapy treatments including deep tissue massage, remedial therapy, lymphatic drainage and kinesiology as well as remedial kinesiology which provides a truly holistic treatment plan for those clients seeking to work towards resolving more long standing physical and emotional negative patterns, by incorporating a variety of therapies, treatment techniques and rehab exercises to resolve dysfunction at the root cause not just treat the symptoms.','Camille de Niese','','publish','open','open','','camille-de-niese-remedial-therapist','','','2010-02-20 18:39:31','2010-02-20 08:39:31','',43,'http://www.dynamicbodytherapy.com/?page_id=62',1,'page','',0),(63,1,'2009-10-06 21:56:07','2009-10-06 11:56:07','Dip.H.Sc. in Remedial Therapy\nDip. Anatomy, Physiology & Massage [London]\nITEC Dip Massage [London]\nAAMT, ANTA, AKA (student member), Network Fitness\n\nWEDNESDAY 12pm - 7:15pm\nTHURSDAY 12pm - 7:15pm\nFRIDAY 12pm - 7:15pm ','Camille de Niese (Remedial Therapist)','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision','','','2009-10-06 21:56:07','2009-10-06 11:56:07','',62,'http://www.dynamicbodytherapy.com/?p=63',0,'revision','',0),(64,1,'2009-10-06 21:54:51','2009-10-06 11:54:51','Dr Shari Trimble\r\nOsteopath, Prescriptive Exercise Consultant\r\nM.H.Sc. [Osteo], B.Sc [Clin], M.C.O.C.A\r\n\r\nMONDAY 1pm - 7pm\r\nWEDNESDAY 1pm - 7pm\r\nFRIDAY 3:15pm - 6:30pm ','Shari Trimble (Osteopath)','','inherit','open','open','','45-re